<div class="about-content section">
<div class="container">
<div class="row">

  <div class="col-md-10 offset-md-1">
  <p><strong>Aging-In-Place Remodeling is a full service remodeling company</strong> that specializes in providing products and services that allow people to stay in the current residence for years to come.&nbsp; Our goal is to create a safe, accessible and comfortable home that blends usability and visual appeal.</p>
  </div>

</div>
</div>
