</div>
</div>
</div>


<div class="testimonials section">
<div class="container">
<h2 class="section-header">People we work with say...</h2>
<div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-6">
    <div class="testimonial-tile">
	<div class="media">
	  <div class="media-left">
		<i class="fa fa-quote-left beginning-quote" aria-hidden="true"></i>
	  </div>
	  <div class="media-body">
		    <p>We had Aging-In-Place Remodeling do some home modifications and install a Stiltz lift in our home. The process was seamless and very professional.</p>
<p>The Stiltz lift was installed in 4 days as promised and provides an easy way for us to go between the floors in our home. The crew that worked on this installation was dedicated to get the job done in 4 days and worked tirelessly to do it. The team communicated well with us and a provided an explanation of how the lift worked and what the service cycle will be.</p>
<p>At the same time as the lift was being installed we had another group of workers widening and moving doorways and performing other modifications on our home. This crew also worked tirelessly, and professionally. The crew were friendly and worked hard every day. Each of them put in a true 8 hour day. Prior to leaving each evening they swept, dusted and mopped the areas they had worked in to ensure we could be comfortable in our home during the time of the modifications.</p>
<p>From my first contact with Tyler Owen to the end of this project, I have been very impressed with this company. The service they offer to anyone wanting to stay in their home, despite aging or illness, is so valuable and I would strongly recommend this company to anyone.</p>
		    <p class="testimonial-author">- Michelle B. &#8211; Rancho Bernardo &#8211; 2024</p>
	  </div>
	</div>
</div> 
    </div>   
      <div class="col-sm-6">
    <div class="testimonial-tile">
	<div class="media">
	  <div class="media-left">
		<i class="fa fa-quote-left beginning-quote" aria-hidden="true"></i>
	  </div>
	  <div class="media-body">
		    <p>Can I say that Aging in Place is Excellent quality, Good Value, Professional, Responsive and On time?<br />
We were looking for an alternative to a stair chair lift and found Tyler Owen and his company, Aging in Place. They have been in business 18 years and know what they are doing. Tyler came out multiple times to work out the plans for where we were going to put the Stiltz lift. He answered all of our questions and worked with us completely. Even answered texts on time. The quoted price was fair. When it came to the install his crew of 2-3 men worked hard and were professional, courteous and treated our home like it was theirs. Six days later our lift was ready to ride. It is quiet, smooth and very high tech. It looks as though it&#8217;s always been there. A huge thank you to Spencer, Nick and the entire team for their experise and congenial can do attitudes! Thank you all!</p>
		    <p class="testimonial-author">- Janet W. &#8211; San Diego &#8211; October 2022</p>
	  </div>
	</div>
</div> 
    </div>   
  </div>
<p class="text-center"><a class="btn btn-default btn-lg btn-view-testimonials" href="/testimonials">Read More Testimonials</a></p>
</div>
</div>

